</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA13d125n1-ptr" id="PJA13d125n1">1</a>

   <p>On 8 July, Jenings wrote to <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>, I take the Liberty of enclosing two Pieces of british Manufacture, neither of which will, I belieeve, pass in the American Markets (<span class="ref-terms">Adams Papers</span>). For more on the bill, see Jenings to <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>, 24 July, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-13-02-0124&amp;expandNote=PJA13d147n3#PJA13d147n3" class="document">note 3</a>, below.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA13d125n2-ptr" id="PJA13d125n2">2</a>

   <p>In the Letterbook copy, <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> underlined the remainder of this sentence and the following one.</p>

